<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Nihar Sanjeev Ilame | Portfolio</title>

<style>
:root{
    --forest-dark:#0f2f25;
    --forest:#1f4d3a;
    --forest-soft:#3a6f5b;
    --tan:#d8c3a5;
    --tan-soft:#f3ede4;
    --text-dark:#1e1e1e;
    --text-muted:#5a5a5a;
    --card-bg:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
}

/* RESET */
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Inter','Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, #e6f0eb, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, #f6efe7, transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--tan-soft), #ffffff);
    color:var(--text-dark);
    line-height:1.7;
    overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* HEADER */
header{
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    flex-direction:column;
    text-align:center;
    position:relative;
}

header::before{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    inset:0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(31,77,58,0.12), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(216,195,165,0.25), transparent 60%);
    z-index:-1;
    animation:slowFloat 14s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

header h1{
    font-size:3.6rem;
    color:var(--forest);
    animation:slideDown 1.2s ease forwards;
}
header h2{
    font-size:1.6rem;
    margin-top:10px;
    color:var(--forest-soft);
    animation:fadeUp 1.4s ease forwards;
}
header p{
    margin-top:12px;
    font-size:1.1rem;
    color:var(--text-muted);
    animation:fadeUp 1.6s ease forwards;
}

header button{
    margin-top:40px;
    padding:15px 44px;
    border:none;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--forest), var(--forest-soft));
    color:white;
    font-size:1rem;
    border-radius:50px;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:0.4s;
    box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(31,77,58,0.35);
    animation:fadeUp 1.8s ease forwards;
}
header button:hover{
    transform:translateY(-4px) scale(1.03);
    box-shadow:0 25px 55px rgba(31,77,58,0.45);
}

/* SECTIONS */
section{
    padding:100px 12%;
}

/* TITLES */
.section-title{
    font-size:2.6rem;
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:70px;
    color:var(--forest);
    position:relative;
}
.section-title::after{
    content:'';
    width:90px;
    height:4px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--forest), var(--tan));
    display:block;
    margin:18px auto 0;
    border-radius:5px;
}

/* GLASS CARDS */
.card{
    background:var(--card-bg);
    backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
    border-radius:26px;
    padding:45px;
    box-shadow:0 25px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    animation:reveal 1.2s ease forwards;
}

/* ABOUT */
.about{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:55px;
}
.about h3{
    font-size:1.8rem;
    margin-bottom:15px;
    color:var(--forest);
}
.about p{
    color:var(--text-muted);
}

/* SKILLS */
.skills{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:40px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.skill{
    width:250px;
    text-align:center;
    animation:float 5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.skill h4{
    font-size:1.5rem;
    color:var(--forest-soft);
}
.skill p{
    margin-top:10px;
    color:var(--text-muted);
}

/* PROJECT */
.project h3{
    font-size:2.1rem;
    color:var(--forest);
    margin-bottom:18px;
}
.project p{
    color:var(--text-muted);
}

/* FREELANCE */
.freelance{
    text-align:center;
}
.freelance p{
    font-size:1.15rem;
    color:var(--text-muted);
}

/* FOOTER */
footer{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--forest-dark), var(--forest));
    color:#e9f2ee;
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
    font-size:0.9rem;
    margin-top:80px;
}

/* ANIMATIONS */
@keyframes slideDown{
    from{transform:translateY(-60px);opacity:0;}
    to{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1;}
}
@keyframes fadeUp{
    from{transform:translateY(50px);opacity:0;}
    to{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1;}
}
@keyframes reveal{
    from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(70px);}
    to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
}
@keyframes float{
    0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);}
    50%{transform:translateY(-12px);}
}
@keyframes slowFloat{
    from{transform:translateY(0);}
    to{transform:translateY(-40px);}
}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:900px){
    .about{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
    }
    header h1{
        font-size:2.5rem;
    }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Nihar Sanjeev Ilame</h1>
    <h2>First Year Computer Science Engineering Student</h2>
    <p>C Programmer • Python Developer • Aspiring Freelancer</p>
    <button onclick="document.getElementById('about').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
        Explore Portfolio
    </button>
</header>

<section id="about">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <div class="about">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Profile</h3>
            <p>
                I am <b>Nihar Sanjeev Ilame</b>, a first year Computer Science Engineering student
                with a strong interest in programming, software development,
                and building clean, logical solutions using <b>C</b> and <b>Python</b>.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Career Objective</h3>
            <p>
                My objective is to grow into a skilled software engineer by
                developing real-world projects, strengthening fundamentals,
                and gaining hands-on experience through <b>freelancing</b> and collaboration.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
    <div class="skills">
        <div class="card skill">
            <h4>C Programming</h4>
            <p>Logic building, fundamentals, problem solving</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card skill">
            <h4>Python</h4>
            <p>Scripting, automation, application development</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card skill">
            <h4>Freelancing</h4>
            <p>Academic & real-world project experience</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Major Project</h2>
    <div class="card project">
        <h3>HerSafer – Women-for-Women Premium Cab Service</h3>
        <p>
            <b>HerSafer</b> is a premium cab service designed exclusively for women,
            operated by women drivers to ensure safety, trust, and comfort.
            <br><br>
            The project emphasizes women empowerment, secure transportation,
            and reliable service through technology-driven solutions.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Freelancing</h2>
    <div class="card freelance">
        <p>
            Open to freelancing in:
            <br>• C Programming  
            <br>• Python Applications  
            <br>• College & startup software projects
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    © 2026 | Nihar Sanjeev Ilame | Computer Science Engineering
</footer>

</body>
</html>
